      "author": "starhunt",
      "description": "## What's Changed\n\n### RPC Payload Update\n- Fix text source payload to match notebooklm-py v0.3.4 format\n- Replace DOM-based notebook list with `wXbhsf` RPC (DOM fallback)\n- Replace DOM-based notebook creation with `CCqFvf` RPC (DOM fallback)\n\n### UI Improvements\n- Add refresh button to notebook select modal\n- Add i18n support: Auto Detect / 한국어 / English\n- All UI strings translated (ribbons, commands, menus, notices, modals, settings)",
